## 📌 Overview

**My CV** is a sleek, animated portfolio application that transforms the traditional paper resume into an immersive mobile experience. Built entirely with Flutter, it combines modern UI design with smooth animations to present professional skills, experience, and projects in a way that truly stands out.

Whether you are a recruiter, collaborator, or fellow developer — this app delivers everything you need to know about Ali Hassan in one polished, interactive package.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🎨 Dynamic Theme Switching
Three hand-crafted color themes to personalize the experience:

| Theme | Color Palette |
|:---|:---|
| 🔵 Classic | Indigo / Blue |
| 🟣 Modern | Purple / Pink |
| 🟢 Creative | Teal / Green |

### 🖼️ Interactive Profile Gallery
- Swipe through multiple profile images with smooth gesture support
- Tap any image to open a full-screen zoom popup

### 💼 Comprehensive Career Overview
- **About Me** — Personal introduction with dynamic skill chips
- **Skills** — Animated progress indicators for AI, Flutter, Web Development & more
- **Experience Timeline** — Clean vertical timeline of professional milestones
- **Projects** — Highlighted key deliverables and live work
- **Education** — Academic background and qualifications

### 📡 Quick Connectivity
- Animated social media shortcut buttons
- One-tap contact cards for email, phone, and messaging

### 🖥️ Modern UI / UX
- Glassmorphism-inspired card and panel design
- Fluid animated containers and seamless page transitions
- Fully responsive Material Design with custom styling and theming

---

