## 📁 Project Structure

```
Cv App/
│
├── lib/
│   ├── main.dart                   # App entry point — theme config & core logic
│   ├── all_widgets_covered.dart    # Full-featured UI widgets and all sections
│   ├── simple_all.dart             # Simplified layout variants
│   └── simplestapp.dart            # Minimal profile implementation
│
├── images/                         # Local assets — profile photos & project visuals
├── 1.jpg                           # Screenshot — Home screen
├── 2.jpg                           # Screenshot — Skills section
├── 3.jpg                           # Screenshot — Experience timeline
├── 4.jpg                           # Screenshot — Projects section
├── 5.jpg                           # Screenshot — Contact screen
├── pubspec.yaml                    # Project dependencies and configuration
└── pubspec.lock                    # Locked dependency versions
```

